254
00:14:35.958 --> 00:14:37.585
Thanks for the insight. genius.

255
00:14:37.835 --> 00:14:38.753
I was...

256
00:14:40.588 --> 00:14:41.798
I was trying to be nice.

257
00:14:41.881 --> 00:14:42.882
Well. you failed.

258
00:14:44.133 --> 00:14:45.134
Well. fuck you.

259
00:14:50.890 --> 00:14:52.642
Dude. seriously.

260
00:14:53.768 --> 00:14:55.728
What's the point of even
attempting with that girl?

261
00:14:55.937 --> 00:14:57.647
Yeah. been there. forgot that.

262
00:14:58.106 --> 00:15:00.066
Don't you need every vote. Marcus?

263
00:15:00.149 --> 00:15:01.275
I don't need that one!

264
00:15:01.359 --> 00:15:03.069
Guys. leave Zach alone.

265
00:15:03.736 --> 00:15:07.156
He's just desperate to lose it before
his dad has to buy him a hooker.

266
00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:08.449
(ALL LAUGH)

267
00:15:08.699 --> 00:15:10.201
You get back here. young man!

268
00:15:10.284 --> 00:15:11.285
Zachy!

269
00:15:11.369 --> 00:15:12.370
Poor Zach!

270
00:15:12.453 --> 00:15:13.454
Yo. Zachy!

271
00:15:14.163 --> 00:15:16.082
HANNAN:
<i>You said something stupid. Zach...</i>

272
00:15:16.541 --> 00:15:17.542
<i>and I yelled at you.</i>

273
00:15:18.167 --> 00:15:19.168
<i>Big deal.</i>

274
00:15:22.422 --> 00:15:23.673
<i>You should have let it go.</i>

275
00:15:25.216 --> 00:15:26.342
<i>But you didn't let it go.</i>

276
00:15:27.802 --> 00:15:29.887
<i>You didn't like that someone told you no.</i>

277
00:15:30.847 --> 00:15:33.391
<i>'Cause guys like you
get anything you want. right?</i>

278
00:15:39.021 --> 00:15:40.273
MATT: You're home early.

279
00:15:44.193 --> 00:15:45.027
Hey.

280
00:15:45.611 --> 00:15:47.071
Come sit with me a minute.

281
00:16:01.461 --> 00:16:02.879
This isn't a talk. is it?

282
00:16:03.337 --> 00:16:04.589
No talk.

283
00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:07.508
We'll communicate through semaphores.

284
00:16:09.218 --> 00:16:12.597
I can see how you'd think I'd be the
one person to laugh at that. but...

285
00:16:13.848 --> 00:16:14.849
Where's your bike?

286
00:16:17.018 --> 00:16:18.019
Uh...

287
