451
00:24:49.571 --> 00:24:50.572
And...

452
00:24:50.864 --> 00:24:52.324
we're having fun up there.

453
00:24:59.999 --> 00:25:01.208
BRYCE: Milady.

454
00:25:01.291 --> 00:25:04.253
HANNAH: <i>Maybe you don't know what
it's like to need a lifeline. Zach.</i>

455
00:25:05.170 --> 00:25:06.171
(BELL RINGS)

456
00:25:14.096 --> 00:25:16.724
<i>The day after you insulted me
in the cafeteria.</i>

457
00:25:16.807 --> 00:25:18.726
<i>my compliment bag was empty.</i>

458
00:25:21.228 --> 00:25:22.604
<i>Not even a cute bunny.</i>

459
00:25:23.480 --> 00:25:24.440
(BELL RINGS)

460
00:25:25.107 --> 00:25:27.359
<i>By the end of the second week.
I knew something was up.</i>

461
00:25:36.076 --> 00:25:38.620
<i>Maybe I should have let it go.
but I didn't.</i>

462
00:25:39.455 --> 00:25:40.706
<i>I wrote you a letter.</i>

463
00:25:41.206 --> 00:25:42.624
<i>I poured my heart out.</i>

464
00:25:42.708 --> 00:25:44.585
<i>opening up about personal things</i>

465
00:25:44.668 --> 00:25:46.837
<i>I hadn't had the courage
to admit to anyone:</i>

466
00:25:47.087 --> 00:25:48.922
<i>How hard life was getting...</i>

467
00:25:49.465 --> 00:25:50.924
<i>how lonely I felt...</i>

468
00:25:51.383 --> 00:25:54.553
<i>and how those stupid compliments
actually meant something to me.</i>

469
00:26:04.062 --> 00:26:05.272
<i>And then I set my trap.</i>

470
00:26:19.578 --> 00:26:21.038
(BELL RINGS)

471
00:26:56.615 --> 00:26:59.243
<i>I was hoping once you read
the letter. you'd get it.</i>

472
00:26:59.326 --> 00:27:02.663
<i>you'd realize how much I needed those
silly things you were stealing from me.</i>

473
00:27:06.708 --> 00:27:08.794
<i>But I guess I wasn't even
worth a reaction.</i>

474
00:27:13.215 --> 00:27:14.299
Why me. Zach?

475
00:27:15.759 --> 00:27:16.844
Why me?

476
00:27:27.312 --> 00:27:28.397
(CHEERING)

477
00:27:30.190 --> 00:27:32.192
Wow. that's double digits already.

478
00:27:38.949 --> 00:27:39.992
(CROWD CHEERS)

479
00:27:54.298 --> 00:27:55.299
Jeez.

480
00:27:55.382 --> 00:27:57.217
Zach is on fire tonight.

481
00:28:02.222 --> 00:28:03.223
Whoo!

482
00:28:05.183 --> 00:28:07.519
(CHANTING) Zach! Zach! Zach! Zach!

483
00:28:20.073 --> 00:28:21.408
(CHANTING CONTINUES) Zach! Zach!

484
00:28:24.494 --> 00:28:28.790
Oh-ho-ho-ho! Yeah!

485
00:28:39.176 --> 00:28:40.177
Stop it!

486
00:28:40.260 --> 00:28:41.345
Stop! Stop it!

487
00:28:41.428 --> 00:28:43.055
Stop playing! Stop the game! Stop!

488
00:28:43.263 --> 00:28:44.932
Stop it! Stop. stop!

489
00:28:54.316 --> 00:28:55.609
STUDENT: Is he crazy?

490
00:29:09.623 --> 00:29:10.874
HANNAH: <i>Why me. Zach?</i>

491
00:29:11.500 --> 00:29:12.709
<i>Why me?</i>

492
00:29:31.186 --> 00:29:32.396
(SCRAPING)

493
00:29:41.363 --> 00:29:42.948
SKYE: Stickin' it to the man!

494
00:29:44.074 --> 00:29:47.452
Or. you know. one particular man
who's rich enough and fucked-up enough

495
00:29:47.536 --> 00:29:49.830
to get his asshole son a $60.000 car.

496
00:29:50.580 --> 00:29:51.957
Skye. what are you...

497
00:29:52.249 --> 00:29:53.542
Are you at the game?

498
00:29:53.959 --> 00:29:55.002
God. no!

499
00:29:57.212 --> 00:29:58.338
Sculpture studio.

500
00:29:58.714 --> 00:30:01.633
It's the only time I can get
the welding rig away from the shop boys.

501
00:30:04.344 --> 00:30:05.470
Were you at the game?

502
00:30:07.389 --> 00:30:08.390
I was.

503
00:30:09.182 --> 00:30:11.643
But it was so bad.
you had to leave before halftime?

504
00:30:15.814 --> 00:30:16.815
I can't...

505
00:30:18.734 --> 00:30:20.068
I can't do this anymore.

506
00:30:21.820 --> 00:30:22.821
This goddamn school.

507
00:30:22.904 --> 00:30:24.114
it's a terrible place.

508
00:30:24.614 --> 00:30:26.992
You're just now coming
to this realization?

509
00:30:28.201 --> 00:30:30.704
Where have you been for
the past three years?

510
00:30:32.331 --> 00:30:33.498
Oh. that's right.

511
00:30:33.582 --> 00:30:34.958
pining after a pretty dead girl.

512
00:30:37.627 --> 00:30:38.545
Why are you so mean?

513
00:30:40.339 --> 00:30:41.798
I thought we were friends.

514
00:30:43.425 --> 00:30:44.426
Were.

515
00:30:45.427 --> 00:30:46.678
We were friends.

516
00:30:48.305 --> 00:30:49.473
What happened?

